body_html:
Not that it is a very helpful advice, and not that I am proud of that fact that it is helpful to me. But:

  • Try restarting the console if you're developing using ipython

Not sure what is it doing wrong, but after few runs with breaks via ctrl+c I encountered the issue. Clearing the scope does not help, but new instance does.

body:
Not that it is a very helpful advice, and not that I am proud of that fact that it is helpful to me. But: 
* Try restarting the console if you're developing using ipython 

Not sure what is it doing wrong, but after few runs with breaks via `ctrl+c` I encountered the issue. Clearing the scope does not help, but new instance does.
